For all of you having the licensing problem, what you do is:
1. Go up to the taskbar.
2. Right click on the time.
3. Click Adjust Date/Time 
4. Set the date back a couple of years, I set it to 2004.
5. Open After Effects a couple of times, after you click accept it will probably stop responding.
6. Reboot.
7. It should work! After you open AE, you can reset the date to 2011, but remember to put it back a couple of years each time you open AE.
